  "train": "all dev rows, plain binary objective on label_c \u2014 no propensity stage, no IPW, no sample weights",
  "protocol": "identical folds/frame/grid-sample/selection as B4 stage 2 (hyperparam_grid.md \u00a75-\u00a76; ES-50 watching v); refit all-dev with fixed n_estimators",
  "dev_seasons": [
    2019,
